channel.title: Help With Port Forward
channel.description:
Hello.. Its about my brothers server again. I got some problems with Port Forwarding.. We can't get to the ip adress.. we were going to www.ipchicken.com and got the ip. and then we pasted it, and setted it into the toolbar.. and it says. "If your computer or network is protected by a firewall or proxy, make sure that Firefox is permitted to access the network."..
So what do i do?, we turned firewall off already.
